race.comment: PRETENTIOUS (8) was out of the placings last time when fifth at this track (20.51) but did record best time of the card when winning three back. Returns to a course where she has performed well. Worth another chance. BUGATTI STEP (1) was in traffic and took a tumble last time but prior to that was a Grade 5 winner in quick time (19.97) at this track in a Grade 5. Must include in calculations. REALITY ZERO (2) placed two back in a Grade 5 at Casino then not far away from a tricky draw last time when fourth (20.31) at this track. Expected to do much better this time. MY WARRIOR (6) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.
